<br>
She was wandering around as a Frost Giant Elite's pet in the NE corner of GD.  We killed the Elite she was following and she despawned.  She immediately spawned in her cave, but before I got there she started heading towards the giant camp.  I can only assume that someone tried to give her the Control Harness while she was wandering and got nowhere because I didn't turn my harness in, yet there she was attacking Grakl.  I shouted to the zone to find out who had turned their harness in, no one answered, so we killed Fergul and he dropped the leggings.<br>
<br>
I had the Control Harness for over a month and hadn't seen her in her cave all that time.  I had seen her wandering, but knew I couldn't do the quest that way.  So for folks in the same position, just kill the giant she is following and then do the quest.  <br>
<br>
BTW, I yelled so loud when I looted the legs that my throat hurts.  =) <p><b><font size=5><font color=blue>Jianna Incessantlydying</font></font></b><BR>
<i><font color=blue>49 High Elf Enchantress</font></i><BR>
<a href=http://www.madbbs.com/users/hallatone><font color=teal>Ancient Ones of Xegony</font></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umissfoxfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miss Foxfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/29/01 12:49:02 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://gwynhyfar.homestead.com/files/face.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Broodmother</span><hr size=1> After observing her odd behavior and spawn times on my server while various people were trying to do either the leggings or wristguard quest, I'd say her spawn on Solusek Ro was more like 8-11 hours. She almost would pop the same time every night. If anyone is waiting for her to spawn, I suggest binding in her room then gating there to check for her.<br>
