When I found her, she was wandering as a dire wolf's pet (strange but true...), i gave her the harness after I did a shout to be sure noone was doing the quest, and I headed to giant fort to wait for her.<br>
<br>
After a long time (6-7 minutes) she engaged the other named, fergul ran away, I followed him, rooted him, BM came to him and attached herself as a pet, and despawned when he died. I looted the legs, stood on my tip-toes and did a dance of joy :)<br>
